namespace SpriteKind {
    export const BestFriend = SpriteKind.create()
}
controller.A.onEvent(ControllerButtonEvent.Pressed, function () {
    if (KinitoPETs_Egg) {
        sprites.destroy(KinitoPETs_Egg)
        if (Kinitos_Dialogue == 0) {
            music.play(music.createSoundEffect(WaveShape.Sine, 1, 5000, 255, 0, 250, SoundExpressionEffect.None, InterpolationCurve.Logarithmic), music.PlaybackMode.InBackground)
            KinitoPET = sprites.create(assets.image`KinitoPET`, SpriteKind.BestFriend)
            game.setDialogFrame(img`
                .....cccccccccccccc.....
                ...cbd111111111111dbc...
                ..cd1111111111111111dc..
                .cd111111111111111111dc.
                .b11111111111111111111b.
                cd11111111111111111111dc
                c1111111111111111111111c
                c1111111111111111111111c
                c1111111111111111111111c
                c1111111111111111111111c
                c1111111111111111111111c
                c1111111111111111111111c
                c1111111111111111111111c
                c1111111111111111111111c
                c1111111111111111111111c
                c1111111111111111111111c
                cd11111111111111111111dc
                .b11111111111111111111b.
                .cd111111111111111111dc.
                ..cd1111111111111111dc..
                ...cbd111d111d1111dbc...
                .....cccccb1bcccccc.....
                ..........c1c...........
                ...........c............
                `)
            game.setDialogCursor(assets.image`KinitoPET Icon`)
            game.showLongText("Hello! I am KinitoPET. Your Virtual friend!", DialogLayout.Bottom)
            Kinitos_Dialogue = 1
            game.setDialogCursor(assets.image`myImage2`)
            game.showLongText("Hello! I'm Dusky!", DialogLayout.Bottom)
            game.setDialogCursor(assets.image`KinitoPET Icon`)
            game.showLongText("Well that's a lovely name! Say, do you mind if I do a friend analysis?", DialogLayout.Bottom)
            game.setDialogCursor(assets.image`myImage2`)
            game.showLongText("What to say?", DialogLayout.Bottom)
            game.showLongText("A=Go ahead! Wait... What’s a friend analysis?", DialogLayout.Bottom)
            game.showLongText("B= I very much do mind.", DialogLayout.Bottom)
            pauseUntil(() => controller.A.isPressed() || controller.B.isPressed())
            if (controller.A.isPressed()) {
                game.setDialogCursor(assets.image`KinitoPET Icon`)
                game.showLongText("A friend analysis is where i quiz you on some topics, like what’s your favorite time of year?", DialogLayout.Bottom)
                if (controller.B.isPressed()) {
                    game.setDialogCursor(assets.image`KinitoPET Icon`)
                    game.showLongText("Wrong answer. You don’t have a choice. We will become friends. Understood?", DialogLayout.Bottom)
                }
            }
        }
    }
})
let KinitoPET: Sprite = null
let Kinitos_Dialogue = 0
let KinitoPETs_Egg: Sprite = null
scene.setBackgroundImage(assets.image`Desktop`)
tiles.setCurrentTilemap(tilemap`level`)
KinitoPETs_Egg = sprites.create(assets.image`Kinitos Egg`, SpriteKind.Player)
